{"id":1734,"date":"2018-07-01T02:55:08","date_gmt":"2018-07-01T02:55:08","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=1734"},"modified":"2021-02-27T08:39:59","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T08:39:59","slug":"cac-loai-son-go-cong-nghiep-pho-bien-nhat-hien-nay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/cac-loai-son-go-cong-nghiep-pho-bien-nhat-hien-nay\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chau chu\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu m\u00e3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang tr\u00ed b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, duy tr\u00ec tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cho c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p. V\u1eady c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u01a1n chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho g\u1ed7 hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m ra sao b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft? N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1o v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00ec h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Byzan chia s\u1ebb \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>T\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a s\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng \u0111i l\u00ean, nhu c\u1ea7u t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng xung quanh c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 t\u0103ng l\u00ean v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 thu\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e3ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t s\u01a1n c\u0169ng tung ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00ec c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u01a1n PU,2K v\u00e0 NC . M\u1ed7i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00f9y theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t g\u1ed7 c\u1ea7n s\u01a1n m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1eebng d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1735\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"817\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son.jpg 540w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-198x300.jpg 198w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><i>S\u01a1n PU<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n PU (Polyurethane) l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n hai th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5 gia \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n PU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng cao b\u00e1m d\u00ednh t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n u\u1ed1n t\u1ed1t, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc b\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb9p trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm, kh\u00f4ng phai m\u00e0u, kh\u00f4ng \u1ed1 v\u00e0ng, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng cao, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. S\u01a1n PU l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 trang tr\u00ed cho b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t g\u1ed7 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0: v\u00e1n \u00e9p, b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tre, n\u1ee9a, m\u00e2y v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u01a1n cho b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kim lo\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1736\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-1-1024x801.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-1-1024x801.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-1-300x235.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-1-768x601.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-1.jpg 1252w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n PU th\u00edch h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean c\u00e1c tr\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh trong nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e1m d\u00ednh b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, s\u01a1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng cao, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c va \u0111\u1eadp m\u1ea1nh tuy nhi\u00ean s\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c dung m\u00f4i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdng cao, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><i>S\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u2013 s\u01a1n 2K<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n 2K l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u01a1n g\u1ed7 cao c\u1ea5p&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 cao c\u1ea5p n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n s\u01a1n v\u00e0 dung m\u00f4i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n 2k s\u1edf h\u1eefu cho m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0: d\u00f2ng s\u01a1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng cao, ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c va \u0111\u1eadp, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, th\u1eddi gian s\u01a1n kh\u00f4 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1 nhanh t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi gian thi c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba chia s\u1ebb \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u01a1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i, ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n 2K c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n m\u00e0u r\u1ea5t cao, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p , b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t sau khi s\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0ng \u1ed1 ngay c\u1ea3 trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u01a1n 2K c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4 l\u00e2u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng s\u01a1n NC cho g\u1ed7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1737\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2.jpg 800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2-300x178.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-2-768x455.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><i>S\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p NC 1 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p NC 1 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u01a1n chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ed3 g\u1ed7 n\u1ed9i, ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p NC 1 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0: s\u01a1n c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao, ti\u1ec7n d\u00f9ng, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho vi\u1ec7c trang tr\u00ed, b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t sau khi s\u01a1n b\u00f3ng s\u00e1ng, s\u01a1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e1m d\u00ednh t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t g\u1ed7 mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb bong tr\u00f3c, r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">S\u01a1n NC c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n t\u1ed1t, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u01a1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng kh\u00f4ng cao, ch\u1ec9 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho g\u1ed7 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00ec khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ed1 v\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1738\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3.jpg 960w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3-300x103.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/cong-nghe-son-3-768x264.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m g\u1ed7 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chau chu\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu m\u00e3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang tr\u00ed b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, duy tr\u00ec tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cho c\u00e1c&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1735,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[29,154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1734","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-goc-bao-chi","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1734","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1734"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1734\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1735"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1734"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1734"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1734"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}